classes.docstring:
"""
    The overlaps_left operator returns true if A's bounding box overlaps or is to the
    left of B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: OverlapsLeftLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'overlaps_right' operator returns true if A's bounding box overlaps or is to the
    right of B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: OverlapsRightLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'overlaps_below' operator returns true if A's bounding box overlaps or is below
    B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: OverlapsBelowLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'overlaps_above' operator returns true if A's bounding box overlaps or is above
    B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: OverlapsAboveLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'left' operator returns true if A's bounding box is strictly to the left
    of B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: LeftLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'right' operator returns true if A's bounding box is strictly to the right
    of B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: RightLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'strictly_below' operator returns true if A's bounding box is strictly below B's
    bounding box.
    """
classes.name: StrictlyBelowLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'strictly_above' operator returns true if A's bounding box is strictly above B's
    bounding box.
    """
classes.name: StrictlyAboveLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The "~=" operator is the "same as" operator. It tests actual geometric
    equality of two features. So if A and B are the same feature,
    vertex-by-vertex, the operator returns true.
    """
classes.name: SameAsLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'bbcontains' operator returns true if A's bounding box completely contains
    by B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: BBContainsLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'bboverlaps' operator returns true if A's bounding box overlaps B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: BBOverlapsLookup

classes.docstring:
"""
    The 'contained' operator returns true if A's bounding box is completely contained
    by B's bounding box.
    """
classes.name: ContainedLookup
